'''Chapel Downs''' is a suburb of [[Auckland]] City in northern New Zealand. It is under local governance of the Auckland Council. The suburb is largely rural but has not become heavily subdivided.{{Citation needed|date=August 2009}} The suburb is in the Howick ward, one of the thirteen administrative divisions of Auckland City, and the area is informally considered East Auckland.
